            <button type="button" onclick="submitConsent()">I Consent to Participate</button>
            <p class="disclaimer">Note: This is a simulated electronic signature. A real eConsent system requires robust security, authentication, and compliance with regulatory standards (e.g., 21 CFR Part 11).</p>
